### Create Rule
POST http://localhost:3000/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "delay30",
  "name": "Delay Alert",
  "condition": {
    "status": "Delayed",
    "beforeDepartureMins": 60
  },
  "messageTemplate": "Flight {{flightNumber}} is delayed. Current status: {{status}}.",
  "isActive": true,
  "createdAt": "2025-04-14T10:00:00Z",
  "updatedAt": "2025-04-14T10:00:00Z"
}

